                        "body": "<div class=\"u-mt-4\"><div class=\"u-mb-3 u-font-bold u-mt-3\">User notes:</div><div class=\"u-mb-3 u-italic u-mt-3\"><span class=\"u-font-bold\">About this chapter: </span> Chapter 12 supplements <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/georgia/irc-2024/chapter/1/scope-and-administration#1\">Chapter 1</a> and establishes the <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/georgia/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#R201.1\">scope</a> of coverage for Chapters <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/georgia/irc-2024/chapter/13/general-mechanical-system-requirements#13\">13</a> through <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/georgia/irc-2024/chapter/24/fuel-gas#24\">24</a>. The applicability of code provisions to existing <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/georgia/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system\">mechanical systems</a> and appliances is established herein.</div><div class=\"u-mb-3 u-italic u-mt-3\"><span class=\"u-font-bold\">Code development reminder:</span> Code change proposals to this chapter will be considered by the IRC\u2014<a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/georgia/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#plumbing\">Plumbing</a>/<a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/georgia/imc-2024\">Mechanical Code</a> Development Committee during the 2024 (Group A) Code&nbsp;Development Cycle.</div></div>",
                        "depth": 0,
                        "diagrams": [],
                        "displayRef": null,
                        "displayTitle": "Chapter 12 Mechanical Administration",
                        "divisionType": "Chapter",
                        "hasAssemblies": false,
                        "isContiguous": true,
